actions.message:
```asciidoc
= Here is your help guide : =
[To have more info on a command type f.help [command]]

[===============================]
[          Help/Info            ]
[===============================]

- f.help to get help
- f.info to get info about the bot and acces to our website

[===============================]
[           Security            ]
[===============================]

- f.gen to generate a code
- f.login (number) to gain access to every channel on the server if you got a good number

[===============================]
[            Staff              ]
[===============================]

- f.warn @Name [reason] to warn someone
- f.warnreset @Name to reset all of the member warn
- f.kick @Name [reason] to kick a member
- f.ban @Name [reason] to ban a member
- f.tempmute @Name [time] to temporaly mute a member
- f.mute @Name to mute a member
- f.unmute @Name to unmute a member
- f.clear [number] to clear message
- f.botinfo to get the info of the bot

[===============================]
[             Fun               ]
[===============================]

- f.request to gain access to the report channel
- f.report @Name [reason] to report someone
- f.love @Name to send a heart at someone
- f.episode to see when there is a new episode
- f.8ball [question] ask and see your answer
- f.roll roll a dice
- f.box @Name to box someone
- f.boop @Name to boop someone
- f.hug @Name to hug someone
- f.metaview [token] to get MetaViewer role
- f.pool [question] to start a pool

[===============================]
[             NSFW              ]
[===============================]

- f.r34 [tag] for a Rule34 image with a tag
- f.r34-bomb [tag] for 5 Rule34 image with a tag
- f.r34-random for a random Rule34 image
- f.e621 [tag] for a e621 image with a tag
- f.e621-bomb [tag] for 5 e621 image with a tag
- f.e621-random for a random e621 image
```
